---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | The Palm Beach Broker">
  <section class="bg-forest py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="font-sans text-gold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-3">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-white font-light leading-tight mb-6">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <div class="w-16 h-px bg-gold mb-8"></div>

      <div class="space-y-8 font-sans text-white/80 leading-relaxed text-base">
        <p>
          Last updated: March 2026. This Privacy Policy describes how THE DANIEYIS GROUP LLC collects,
          uses, and protects your information when you use our website or real estate services.
        </p>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-gold font-light mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>
            We may collect your name, email address, phone number, property preferences, and any
            information you provide when contacting us or completing forms on our website.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-gold font-light mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>
            We use your information to provide real estate services, respond to inquiries, send
            property alerts and marketing communications, and improve our website.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-gold font-light mb-3">
            3. Text Messages and Emails (SMS Opt-In)
          </h2>
          <p>
            By submitting your contact information, you agree to receive calls, emails, and text
            messages from THE DANIEYIS GROUP LLC related to real estate services. Message and data
            rates may apply. Message frequency may vary. You can opt out at any time by replying
            STOP to any text message or using the unsubscribe link in our emails.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-gold font-light mb-3">4. Sharing of Information</h2>
          <p>
            We do not sell your personal information. We may share it with service providers who
            help us operate our business, or as required by law.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-gold font-light mb-3">
            5. Terms and Conditions - SMS Services
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 pl-4 border-l-2 border-gold/30">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Consent for SMS Communication</h3>
              <p>
                Information obtained as part of the SMS consent process will not be shared with third
                parties for marketing purposes.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Types of SMS Communications</h3>
              <p>
                If you consent to receive text messages, you may receive messages related to appointment
                reminders, follow-up messages, and billing inquiries.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Message Frequency</h3>
              <p>Message frequency may vary depending on your interactions with us.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Potential Fees</h3>
              <p>
                Standard message and data rates may apply depending on your mobile carrier plan.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Opt-In Method</h3>
              <p>
                You may opt in to receive SMS messages by submitting a website form or otherwise
                providing express consent to communicate with you.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Opt-Out Method</h3>
              <p>
                You can opt out at any time by replying STOP to any SMS message. You may also contact
                us directly to request removal from text communications.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Help</h3>
              <p>
                Reply HELP to any text message for assistance, or contact us through our website.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-gold font-light mb-3">6. Data Security</h2>
          <p>
            We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information, but no method of
            transmission over the internet is completely secure.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-gold font-light mb-3">7. Your Choices</h2>
          <p>
            You may contact us at any time to update your information, opt out of communications, or
            request that we delete your personal data where applicable by law.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-gold font-light mb-3">8. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact THE DANIEYIS GROUP LLC
            through the contact information provided on this website.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
